data.description: Discover refined living in this three-bedroom, two-full-bathroom haven nestled in the heart of Sugar Pond. The enchanting backyard, complete with a sparkling pool, sets the stage for outdoor bliss. Embrace peace of mind with a newer roof and impact windows, while inside, tasteful upgrades adorn every corner, creating a space where modern elegance meets timeless charm. Your dream home awaits, combining functionality and aesthetic appeal effortlessly.
